---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title={`About | ${SITE.name}`} description="Meet Patryk, the founder of VettedPick: honest budget alternatives to viral and luxury products.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">About VettedPick</h1>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-start">
      <div class="flex h-32 w-32 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-100 to-brand-200 text-4xl font-bold text-brand-700">
        P
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Hi, I'm Patryk.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          I started VettedPick because I was sick of overpaying for branded items that looked great
          on Instagram but didn't match the hype in real life. Like a lot of people, I kept seeing
          the same viral products everywhere: $500 headphones, $200 lamps, $300 backpacks, and
          wondering if the budget version was actually terrible or genuinely good enough.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          So I started testing. Reading thousands of reviews, comparing specs, and tracking down the
          Amazon picks that real shoppers actually love. VettedPick is where I share those findings,
          no fluff, no fake urgency, just honest comparisons so you can get the same vibe for less.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          When you click through to Amazon from this site, I may earn a small commission at no extra
          cost to you. That helps keep VettedPick running and lets me keep testing new products.
          I only recommend picks I'd genuinely consider buying myself.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our mission</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Help smart shoppers in the US find budget-friendly alternatives to viral and luxury products
        with transparent reviews, clear comparisons, and full affiliate disclosures.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
